MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-2326. Reitz v. Mathews.

Franklin County, No. 94APE01-15. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective January 9, 1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
